imdb.title: Housing Complex C
imdb.plot: Follows Kimi, as trouble seems to follow her wherever she goes, and now horrific incidents begin to happen in the small housing complex where she lives - is an ancient evil stalking the residents of Housing Complex C?

episodes.title: Optical Illusion
episodes.plot: Everything in Housing Complex C has always seemed fine. Until a new batch residents move in, and some strange incidents occur. Is their arrival just a coincidence?

episodes.title: Mismatched Buttons
episodes.plot: Kim wants to get along with the other new residents, and hopes a shaved ice party will help break the ice, but there's something odd in the syrup.

episodes.title: The Wheel Comes Full Circle
episodes.plot: As more and more bizarre events occur, everyone is becoming concerned. Kimi and some of the older residents explore the ruins under the complex in search of what might be causing all of these incidents.

episodes.title: The End of the Line
episodes.plot: There's definitely something wrong, but the old residents didn't seem to notice. The new arrivals will help unveil the horror that's been lurking all along.
